About Framework: - This is scalable framework.
This framework contains of BDD concepts with respective to Rest Assured terminologies.

It comprises of : 
Baseclass-Generic Functions and objects to be used.
Test Runner- Main class to initiate the API under test.
Feature File-Consists of Acceptane and Regression test cases.
Step Defination- Defines the feature to carry assertions.
Properties file -Consist of config data.
HTML file- Report.

How to use:
Just run the test runner class as junit.

Report Viweing: 
Just go to target folder of src project and access the index.html
